📊 SmartInvest
Real-Time Risk Assessment System for Portfolio Optimization using ML & Financial APIs
🚀 Overview
SmartInvest is a modern fintech web application that helps users make data-driven investment decisions by combining:

📈 Financial Analysis

🤖 Machine Learning Predictions

📊 Portfolio Optimization

⚠️ Risk Assessment

The platform provides an interactive dashboard where users can analyze stocks, evaluate risk, and optimize their portfolio efficiently.

🎯 Problem Statement
Investors often struggle with:

Understanding market trends

Balancing risk vs return

Choosing optimal stock combinations

Interpreting technical indicators

SmartInvest solves this by providing intelligent insights instead of raw data.

✨ Key Features
📊 Dashboard
Portfolio overview (AUM, Risk Score, Volatility)

Interactive charts

ML-based predictions

📈 Market Analysis
Stock price visualization

Technical indicators (MA, RSI, etc.)

Trend analysis

🥧 Portfolio Optimization
Multi-stock selection

Allocation visualization (Pie Chart)

Optimized portfolio suggestions

⚠️ Risk Analysis
Sharpe Ratio

Sortino Ratio

Volatility

Max Drawdown

🔮 Simulation
Future portfolio prediction

Growth visualization

📜 History & Triggers
Signal-based insights

Event timeline

Model reasoning

🧠 Tech Stack
💻 Frontend
React (Vite)

Tailwind CSS

Recharts

Lucide Icons

⚙️ Backend
Python

Pandas, NumPy

Scikit-learn

🤖 Machine Learning
Random Forest Regressor

Feature Engineering (MA, Volatility, Momentum)

🌐 APIs
Yahoo Finance (yfinance)

⚙️ How It Works
📥 Fetch stock data using APIs

🧹 Preprocess and generate features

🤖 Train ML model

📊 Predict returns

📈 Visualize insights on dashboard

🧠 Generate recommendations

